precis:
Amendments to the NATIONAL TRAINING REGULATIONS which will increase the
amount of the basic and supplementary benefits payable to adults who attend
an occupational training course or program and will introduce a new section
intitled "Disability Allowance" (section 6), effective February 3, 1991.
